 (x-\frac{r}{4})^2 + (y-b)^2 - \frac{r^2}{16} = x^2 + y^2 - r^2 
 x  -\frac{r}{4} + y -b = x + y - \sqrt{\frac{15}{16}}r 
 -\frac{r}{4} = - \sqrt{\frac{15}{16}}r +b 
 (\sqrt{\frac{15}{16}}-\sqrt{\frac{1}{16}})r =  b 
 \frac{\sqrt{15}-1}{4} = b 
